---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import GlassHero from "../../components/GlassHero.astro";
const updated = "April 20, 2026";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="CaloricLab privacy policy. Learn how we handle (and don't collect) your personal health data."
  noindex={false}
>
  <!-- Page header — liquid glass -->
  <GlassHero title="Privacy Policy">
    <p slot="below" class="mt-2 text-xs text-white/40">Last updated: {updated}</p>
  </GlassHero>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10 sm:py-14">
    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none prose-headings:font-bold prose-headings:tracking-tight prose-a:text-green-700">

      <p>At CaloricLab ("we," "us," or "our"), your privacy is important to us. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and how we protect it.</p>

      <h2>Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
      <p>All calculations on CaloricLab are performed <strong>entirely in your browser</strong>. When you enter your age, weight, height, or other personal measurements into our calculators, that data is never sent to our servers. We have no access to your health data.</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect Automatically</h2>
      <p>Like most websites, we collect standard analytics data when you visit CaloricLab, including:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Pages visited and time spent on pages</li>
        <li>Referring URLs (how you found us)</li>
        <li>Browser type and operating system</li>
        <li>Approximate geographic location (country/region level only)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>This information is collected in aggregate and cannot be used to identify you personally.</p>

      <h2>Advertising</h2>
      <p>CaloricLab is supported by display advertising. Our advertising partners may use cookies to show you relevant ads. You can opt out of personalized advertising through your browser settings or through the Network Advertising Initiative opt-out page.</p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use cookies for analytics and advertising purposes. Essential cookies are required for the site to function. You can disable non-essential cookies in your browser settings, though this may affect your experience.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use third-party services including analytics and advertising platforms. These services have their own privacy policies governing how they handle data.</p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>CaloricLab is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We'll note the last updated date at the top of this page.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this policy? Email us at <a href="mailto:privacy@caloriclab.com">privacy@caloriclab.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
